TextEng: I've got another drink order.
Text: 음료 주문이 또 들어왔네.

TextEng: What would you like?
Text: 뭐 드릴까?

TextEng: I know you're good, honey. I was just thinking you might be thirsty.
Text: 알아, 됐다는 거. 그냥 목마를까 싶었지, 자기.

TextEng: All right, but no loiterin'.
Text: 좋아, 하지만 얼쩡거리지 말라고.

TextEng: Our regulars are made-up of Elaith, Wanev, Alhelor, Ander, Albie, Darktongue, and Peren. Alhelor's a merchant, Wanev's a wizard, and Ander's just a boy. The rest think of themselves as adventurers. 'Cept Elaith. He's just an elf.
Text: 단골은 엘레이스, 와네브, 알헬러, 앤더, 앨비, 다크텅, 페렌이야. 알헬러는 상인, 와네브는 마법사, 앤더는 그냥 애지. 나머지는 다들 자기가 모험가래. 엘레이스만 빼고. 걘 그냥 엘프야.

TextEng: Sure thing, hon. Anything else?
Text: 좋아, 자기. 더 필요해?

TextEng: If you say so. Anything else?
Text: 그래, 알았어. 또 뭐 필요해?

TextEng: He's a dangerous-looking one, ain't he. Not mean, though - Just protective of that little girl of his. Anyone else?
Text: 그 사람, 위험하게 생겼지. 못된 건 아니고... 그 꼬마 딸 지키는 데만 죽자사자더라. 또 누구?

TextEng: Yeah, looks like he's left. I wasn't on duty but one of the girls said there was a commotion, a bit of magic, and he was gone... Anyone else?
Text: 그래, 떠난 것 같아. 난 근무가 아니었는데, 딴 애 말로는 소동이 좀 있었고, 마법도 쓰더니 사라졌다더라... 또 누구?

TextEng: Lecherous old bastard, he is! Keeps staring down my blouse every time I wipe tables. Anyone else?
Text: 음탕한 늙은이야, 완전! 내가 테이블을 닦을 때마다 가슴만 뻔히 쳐다본다니까. 또 누구?

TextEng: Aye, he's gone for the night, thank goodness. Must have found some fool lass to take home with him. Anyone else?
Text: 응, 오늘 밤은 갔어, 다행히도. 어리석은 아가씨 하나 꼬셔서 데려갔겠지. 또 누구?

TextEng: Him? He showed up shortly before Sir Karathis led all those poor boys astray. A bit of a werewolf hunter himself, it seems. Anyone else?
Text: 그 사람? 카라디스 경이 그 불쌍한 애들을 꼬드기기 직전에 나타났지. 본인도 무슨 늑대인간 사냥꾼 같더라. 또 누구?

TextEng: He left a while back, looking tired. Check with Ander, I'm sure he has a better idea where old Alhelor went. Anyone else?
Text: 좀 전에 피곤해 보이면서 나갔어. 앤더에게 물어봐, 알헬러 영감이 어디 갔는지 그쪽이 더 잘 알 거야. 또 누구?

TextEng: Poor chap, that one. Had all 'is friends turned into werewolves and now he hangs about here, helping that Alhelor pawn his wares. Anyone else?
Text: 그 사람, 참 딱하지. 친구들이 전부 늑대인간이 돼 버려서 지금은 여기서 알헬러의 물건을 파는 걸 돕고 있어. 또 누구?

TextEng: He ain't here, is he... That's strange. Ever since the incident, he's been scared to set foot outside the place. Anyone else?
Text: 여기 없지... 이상하네. 그 일 이후로는 겁나서 가게 밖으로는 발도 못 내딛었거든. 또 누구?

TextEng: The little guy? He's new here, like you. Seems like a nice enough fellow, if a little too smart for his own good sometimes. Anyone else?
Text: 그 조그만 친구? 너처럼 신참이야. 괜찮은 사람 같긴 한데 가끔 너무 아는 척을 하더라. 또 누구?

TextEng: He checked out a little while back. He seemed obsessed with the goings-on in Thundertree, so maybe you can find him there. Anyone else?
Text: 조금 전에 나갔어. 선더트리에서 벌어지는 일에 꽂힌 눈치더라. 거기서 찾아보는 게 나을 거야. 또 누구?

TextEng: The dwarf fellow, right? Yeah, he's new and cheap as a rat-ridden bed! Five ales and counting and not a single tip! Anyone else?
Text: 그 드워프 말이지? 맞아, 신참인데 쥐 들끓는 침대만큼이나 짠돌이야! 에일을 다섯 잔이나 마시고 팁은 한 푼도 안 줬다니까! 또 누구?

TextEng: Hmph. He left without settlin' his account. Said he had some leads in Luskan. Good riddance, I say. Anyone else?
Text: 쳇. 계산도 안 하고 나가더라. 러스칸에 단서가 있다나 뭐라나. 잘 가라지. 또 누구?

TextEng: Aye, now there's a gentleman if ever I knew one. Always a please and thank you, ma'am, and a few extra coins on the table. Anyone else?
Text: 아, 그 사람은 정말 신사야. 늘 '부탁해요, 고마워요'는 기본에, 탁자 위에 동전도 몇 닢 더 놔두고 가거든. 또 누구?

TextEng: He said he was off to see the Wood. Told me he'd be back soon but no word of him. I hope the good fellow's all right. Anyone else?
Text: 숲에 다녀온다더니 곧 돌아온다 했는데 소식이 없네. 그 착한 영감, 무사했으면 좋겠다. 또 누구?

TextEng: Coming right up...
Text: 금방 가져갈게...

TextEng: I'm afraid we have to cut you off until you've sobered up a bit.
Text: 미안하지만, 좀 정신 차릴 때까지는 더 못 줘.

TextEng: Sorry, you don't have enough gold on you.
Text: 미안해, 금화가 모자라.

TextEng: Sure. Let me tell you who they are, and then you can tell me who you're curious about. Sound fair, handsome?
Text: 좋아. 누가 누군지 먼저 말해 줄게. 그다음에 누구 얘기가 궁금한지 말해. 괜찮지, 잘생긴 양반?

TextEng: Sure. Let me tell you who they are, and then you can tell me who you want the gossip on. Sound fair?
Text: 좋아. 누가 누군지 먼저 말해 줄게. 그다음에 누구 뒷얘기를 듣고 싶은지 말해. 괜찮지?
